HEADWORD: Weroole
<hw>We*roo"le</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>An Australian lorikeet (<spn>Ptilosclera versicolor</spn>) noted
for the variety of its colors; -- called also <altname>varied
lorikeet</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

